                (<span class="text-ambar font-bold">Ver Peixes</span>)</a>
            <a href="/como-preparar"
                class="block px-3 py-3 rounded-md text-base font-medium text-white hover:bg-slate-800 hover:text-ambar border-b border-slate-700 last:border-0 min-h-[44px]">Como
